{{DISPLAYTITLE:LVDW_EWALD}}
{{TAGDEF|LVDW_EWALD|logical|.FALSE.}}

Description: {{TAG|LVDW_EWALD}} decides whether the lattice summation in <math>E_{disp}</math> expression by means of Ewald's summation is computed.
----
{{TAG|LVDW_EWALD}} decides whether the lattice summation in <math>E_{disp}</math> expression by means of Ewald's summation is computed in the pairwise van der Waals corrections schemes [[DFT-D2]], [[DFT-ulg]] and [[Tkatchenko-Scheffler_method|Tkatchenko-Scheffler method]].

